title: Morning Joe 1/18/21
description: The FBI is vetting all of the 25,000 National Guard troops coming into D.C. for the inauguration due to fears of an insider attack. Meanwhile, New Yorker footage shows new images of the chaos during the Capitol siege.
author: news.podcasts@nbcuni.com (NBC News)
